Lady Gaga showed up in true Versace girl style wearing a straight-out-the-runway sheer corset Versace gown, and Cara Delevingne, days after coming out with her sobriety journey, arrived in style in a red Elie Saab Haute Couture dress, channelling old Hollywood vibes.